<template>
  <drawner-bar :tabs="tabs" />
</template>

<script>
export default {
  components: { DrawnerBar: () => import("@/components/DrawnerBar.vue") },
  data() {
    return {
      tabs: {
        items: []
      }
    };
  },
  beforeMount: function() {
    let vm = this;
    if (!(localStorage.getItem("isSign") === "true" ? true : false)) {
      vm.$router.replace("/error/403");
    }

    let roleName = localStorage.getItem("roleName");
    if (roleName != "ROLE_ADMIN") {
      if (roleName == "ROLE_MANAGER") {
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Dashboard",
          router: "/manager/dashboard"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Account Setting",
          router: "/manager/edit-account/profile"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Host Pending",
          router: "/manager/hosts"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Home Pending",
          router: "/manager/homes"
        });
      } else if (roleName == "ROLE_HOST") {
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Dashboard",
          router: "/host/dashboard"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "My Homes",
          router: "/host/homes"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Account Setting",
          router: "/ds"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Messages",
          router: "/dsdsds"
        });
      } else if (roleName == "ROLE_USER") {
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "My Bookings",
          router: "/me/bookings"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Messages",
          router: "/hdfdsfds"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Account Setting",
          router: "/me/edit-account/profile"
        });
        vm.tabs.items.push({
          title: "Wishlist",
          router: "/dsdsdsff"
        });
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style>
</style>
